{"tid":417620,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"求一首失傳左既音樂, 我搵極都搵唔返","createTime":"2017-09-28T23:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T15:28:15.000Z","uid":112459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0534bd7836c41b91d9604a8aa8b25320454a91d","tid":417620,"uid":112459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:56:52.000Z","msg":"如果有邊位巴絲以前有聽過開903 既節目<br />\n2007年做既節目  叫做 乜野地獄 <br />\n(主持 我記得係 阿喱&quot;張家豐&quot; )<br />\n如果記錯節目既話 可能我個時聽既係  阿喱做過既 大野禪寺 <br />\n正題係<br />\n有冇人知道 係以上提及到既節目入面<br />\n節目開頭通常會播既個一段頹廢到仆街既background music 係咩<br />\n求名求Link又求seed<br />\n<br />\nJJ插沙跪地求有神手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c1eede3fbb93a50276055d37dba683f19c63b8","tid":417620,"uid":112459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:00:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fcfb7ae6210dd92f8b5e269c182fbf93d6c7fc03","tid":417620,"uid":112459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:05:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69c35391fee28e6ef3d322aa1c5beeb469dfc3ef","tid":417620,"uid":112459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c10a334cb526f437a2557ca24b0b53a2d554f659","tid":417620,"uid":112459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:20:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c749bd5091ff17f9df4111654a6339e8898f574d","tid":417620,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:24:23.000Z","msg":"搭單<br />\n人人人 同 你睇我唔到 片頭曲係咩"},{"pid":"fb14a2933a81ebdc346fa5d9ad7588c9d4e4ceca","tid":417620,"uid":112459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:38:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"362396cc1217aa85c26da4d177a20d7e8d60d091","tid":417620,"uid":112459,"l